title: Haguth-Khol
body:
History

Origin - The Age of Creation

Urunine makes Haguth-Khol and the other Hagalisk.

Appearance

Hagath-Khol shares a similar appearance to the rest of the Hagalisk. However, he is swifter than his counterparts, but not as strong. He has only two horns that protrude on either side like antlers, but they are much longer than the similar ones found on Hagann-Tante.
preface: Haguth-Khol is one of the three Hagalisk.

title: Haguth-Khol
body:
History

Origin - The Age of Creation

Urunine makes Haguth-Khol and the other Hagalisk.

The Age of Races & The War of the Beasts

Haguth-Khol and the other Hagalisk are called upon by Urunine to fight in The War of the Beasts.
